    helpPosition: 'right',
    helpText: 'High-throughput phenotypic profiling (HTPP) with the Cell Painting assay (Nyffeler et al. 2020, PMID: <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31899216/" title="Bioactivity screening of environmental chemicals using imaging-based high-throughput phenotypic profiling" target="_blank" rel="noopener">31899216</a> ). Please see the assay description for details.',
